## Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|---|---|
| `StepperSeparator` takes a `step` prop and lives between items | Cleaner layout in flex-row; mirrors how most real-world steppers work |
| `StepperPanel` inside `StepperItem` | Follows Accordion pattern; works in vertical mode; visible in horizontal mode only for active step |
| `data-active`/`data-completed` as presence attributes | Allows clean `data-[active]:` Tailwind selectors; React omits `undefined` attributes from DOM |
| `mt-4` on horizontal separator | Positions separator center at ~16px from top, aligning with center of `size-8` (32px) indicator |
| `ml-[15px]` on vertical separator | Centers the 2px separator under the 32px indicator circle (16px center - 1px half-width = 15px) |
| `ml-11` on vertical panel | Matches indicator width (32px = `size-8`) + gap (12px = `gap-3`) = 44px = `ml-11` |
| No Radix dependency | Component is fully custom, no Radix primitives needed |

